My Thought's,I feel that while this sight will probebly be a constant sore spot for many,it helps to get things out in the open,such as, is especially true in my case and I suspect for many more.I am home alone and have lost the ability to function in the world outside,what I mean in saying by this is that I can not guarentee my actions in the public sector,there are paths that are blocked by something that happened I guess when a bullet entered into my head in 1967,and I loose control and believe me,it isn't a pretty sight.Here I feel like I am among friend's,also I need to appologize to Oxyman.I am truly sorry that I lashed out at YOU.You have every right to say what YOU FEEL,I hope you can forgive me.I could say that after all I am a Psycho but that doesn't set with me.My wife &amp; Family &amp; I watch PBS often and I pray that they will be able to continue there fine work,I do not fully trust them,but more than any other media.The very most important thing at this site is that some people have taken the time to give a small place in this huge planet called earth for some who share a truth,that this is a world that can absorbe the essence of one's soul by division.Here you can say how you see things,while another can do the same.One could consider this site a battle ground  where there are no physical confrontations nor blow's struct.We have an oppotunity to express truth's,hope's,dream's,desire's.I truly believe that most of us are somewhere in the middle,we should make every attempt to read what the others are saying with an open mind,afterall arren't we all human.We veterans I believe are trying to give an account of what actually happened and hopefully what did will be seen and prevented in the future,none of us can buy a ticket to the past.May WE all remember that every person in this country is the Government and WE are ALL responsible for it's action's!!Those at the very top are not stupid,they know very well that if they can divide YOU and I then they can do as they wish.It's YOUR CHOICE,I suggest we all look closely at what is really going on and get out the LETTER'S/VOTE'S!Please let's keep this site open and the information flowing???
